Civil rights activist stress following important aspect with regard to the law.
Only migrants with legal status must take the test.
You do not have this status there is no check and therefore no official work.
Meanwhile the bulk of migrant workers is still illegal in Russia.
"Welcome" or "Access for unauthorized persons prohibited"
Many migrants to confirm that it is not easy to get an official status in Russia.
Bureaucratic hurdles and of course the language difficulties are the reason.
Also, the legalization costs money: 12 16 thousand rubles up to.
