"Only spare no costs for false papers"
Already on the day on which the Act came into force, turned out that not only the registration documents of migrants can be faked.
Some fake certificates, which certify the completion of the language tests were taken by employees of the Federal Migration Service fitting.
The fake documents were printed with a normal colour printer.
Of course the new owners received it not in vain: every migrant, who hoped to be able to save yourself so the tests, paid seven thousand rubles for the document.
This is more than twice as much as the cost of the official test: it costs three thousand rubles a migrant workers.
